'''Eskişehir Caricature Museum''' is a museum in [[Eskişehir]], [[Turkey]] The museum is in [[Odunpazarı]] [[ilçe]] (second level municipality) of Eskişehir at {{coord|39|45|57|N|30|31|32|E}}. It is in a neighborhood of museums.
The building is a residence house built in 1900s. It was restored and used as a museum of [[Anadolu University]]. Its total service area is {{convert|265|m2}}. Each room of the house is dedicated to different displays such as, permanent display, temporary display, Eskişehir caricaturists’ display, portraits of famous caricaturists etc. There is also a library in the museum <ref>[http://www.ekm.anadolu.edu.tr/about_museum.htm Anadolu University page]</ref>
