'''''Mirages: The Unexpurgated Diary of Anaïs Nin, 1939-1947''''' is a volume of diary entries by [[Anaïs Nin]] from her life between 1939 and 1947, first published in 2013 by [[Swallow Press]].<ref>{{cite web|work=Amazon|url=https://www.amazon.com/Mirages-Unexpurgated-Diary-Anaïs-1939/dp/0804011656/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1507340909&sr=1-1&keywords=mirages%3A+the+unexpurgated+anais|title=Mirages: The Unexpurgated Diary of Anaïs Nin, 1939–1947 Paperback|accessdate=October 4, 2017}}</ref> It was edited by Paul Herron, and features an introduction by [[Kim Krizan]].
